Package: OptionMonteCarlo
Type: Package
Title: Monte Carlo Simulation Methods for Option Pricing
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-01-09
Author: Jakub Wujec
Maintainer: Jakub Wujec <kuba1302@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides tools for pricing financial derivatives, particularly options, using Monte Carlo simulation methods. It enables users to compute prices for various types of options under different market conditions, focusing on accuracy and computational efficiency.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.5)
